<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KickDepression - Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        aside {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        main {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .form-section {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        .form-section h2 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        input {
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            outline: none;
        }
        button {
            padding: 12px;
            background: #ff4081;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        button:hover {
            background: #e60073;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>KickDepression</h1>
        <p>Your Path to a Happier Life</p>
    </header>
    
    <aside>
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>We help individuals overcome depression and guide youth towards a positive future. Our experienced consultants provide professional support to improve mental well-being.</p>
    </aside>
    
    <main>
        <section class="form-section">
            <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <label for="image">Upload Image:</label>
                <input type="file"  name="imagefile" >
               <button>upload</button>
            </form>
        </section>
        <section class="form-section">
            <h2>Hire a Consultant</h2>
           
            <form action="/create" method="post"  >
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

                <label for="age">DOB:</label>
                <input type="text" id="age" name="age" required>

                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="text" id="email" name="email" required>

                <label for="mobile">Mobile:</label>
                <input type="number" id="mobile" name="mobile" required>

                
                <button >Submit</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>Contact us at: <a href="mailto:ak8861433@gmail.com" style="color: #ff4081;">ak8861433@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p>&copy; 2025 KickDepression. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
